item.title: Another Dismal Loss vs. a Division Rival...What Now?
item.description: Jeff Blair and Kevin Barker break down the Blue Jays' 6-1 loss vs. the Orioles at Rogers Centre. They take your calls, and get to the offensive woes rearing their ugly heads once again - what, if anything, can be changed about that? Is it as simple as changing hitting coaches, or is there something more there? They discuss the mounting losses within the division, if the AL East is already lost, and what to expect out of the team heading into another important series vs. Boston at Fenway Park...
